<item>
            <title>[DERBY-4659] Allow routines to take arguments of BOOLEAN type</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4659</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should allow routines to take BOOLEAN arguments as part of our expanding support for the BOOLEAN datatype.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
